 with external perturbations, contrasts with the thick disks of other\nminor body belts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Feb 2005 21:06:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2005 15:32:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
