ental data on nucleon-nucleon scattering. The properties of the deuteron\nthat were calculated by using various approximations of the effective-range\nfunction comply well with their experimental values.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Feb 2005 01:04:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
